    <title>Markdown样式示例</title>
    <link href="http://yoursite.com/2018/08/01/Markdown%E6%A0%B7%E5%BC%8F%E7%A4%BA%E4%BE%8B/"/>
    <id>http://yoursite.com/2018/08/01/Markdown样式示例/</id>
    <published>2018-07-31T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-02-02T15:48:02.318Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>Markdown</strong>是一种轻量级<strong>标记语言</strong>，它以纯文本形式(<em>易读、易写、易更改</em>)编写文档，并最终以HTML格式发布。</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="这是一级标题"><a href="#这是一级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是一级标题"></a>这是一级标题</h1><h2 id="这是二级标题"><a href="#这是二级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是二级标题"></a>这是二级标题</h2><h3 id="这是三级标题"><a href="#这是三级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是三级标题"></a>这是三级标题</h3><h4 id="这是四级标题"><a href="#这是四级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是四级标题"></a>这是四级标题</h4><h5 id="这是五级标题"><a href="#这是五级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是五级标题"></a>这是五级标题</h5><h6 id="这是六级标题"><a href="#这是六级标题" class="headerlink" title="这是六级标题"></a>这是六级标题</h6><p><strong>这是加粗的文字</strong><br><em>这是倾斜的文字</em><br><strong><em>这是斜体加粗的文字</em></strong><br><del>这是加删除线的文字</del></p><p>东莱很快就感染了，接着就是尚州，离都城汉阳也就一步之遥。</p><p>两条主线合二为一。</p><p>另外，细心一点，会发现这部分有些情节和《釜山行》有异曲同工之处。比如当地有权势的人都跑到船上避难，偏偏一个老太婆因思念儿子，把变成丧尸的儿子带到船上，船上的人几乎团灭。</p><blockquote><p>这是引用的内容</p><blockquote><p>这是引用的内容</p></blockquote></blockquote><blockquote><p>这是引用的内容</p></blockquote><p><a href="http://baidu.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">百度</a></p><p><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/u/1f5ac0cf6a8b" target="_blank">简书</a></p><ul><li>无序列表<ul><li>无序列表<ul><li>无序列表</li><li>无序列表</li><li>无序列表</li></ul></li><li>无序列表<ol><li>有序列表有序列表有序列表有序列表</li><li>有序列表有序列表有序列表有序列表有序列表有序列表</li><li>有序列表</li></ol></li></ul></li><li>无序列表</li><li>无序列表</li></ul><ol><li>有序列表</li><li>有序列表</li><li>有序列表</li></ol><table><thead><tr><th>姓名</th><th>技能</th><th>排行</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>刘备</td><td>哭</td><td>大哥</td></tr><tr><td>关羽</td><td>打</td><td>二哥</td></tr><tr><td>张飞</td><td>骂</td><td>三弟</td></tr></tbody></table><figure class="highlight python hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment"># python</span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">lower = int(input(<span class="hljs-string">"输入区间最小值: "</span>))</span><br><span class="line">upper = int(input(<span class="hljs-string">"输入区间最大值: "</span>))</span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> num <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> range(lower,upper + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> num &gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> range(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,num):</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (num % i) == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">                <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">            print(num)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight javascript hljs"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="hljs-comment">// javascript</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">var</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,len=cars.length;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (; i&lt;len; i++)</span><br><span class="line">&#123; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="hljs-built_in">document</span>.write(cars[i] + <span class="hljs-string">"&lt;br&gt;"</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>create database hero</code></p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Markdown&lt;/strong&gt;是一种轻量级&lt;strong&gt;标记语言&lt;/strong&gt;，它以纯文本形式(&lt;em&gt;易读、易写、易更改&lt;/em&gt;)编写文档，并最终以HTML格式发布。&lt;/p&gt;
    
    </summary>
    
    
      <category term="markdown" scheme="http://yoursite.com/tags/markdown/"/>
    
